title: Dungeons and Dragons Therapy Session #1
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda and Humberto play Dungeons and Dragons with Adam Johns and Adam Davis from Game to Grow - a non-profit dedicated to spreading the use of games in therapy and other helpful settings.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

Aug 10, 2018.

Email: Contact@PsychologyInSeattle.com

List of all episodes: https://psychologyinseattle.squarespace.com/list-of-episodes
